3. Real-Time WebSocket Synchronization Engine
To support instantaneous cross-device communication without performance degradation under load, the application tier abstracts connection mapping via a Redis Pub/Sub cluster. This layer guarantees that when a backend worker instance processes an operational event, every connected node shifts state within milliseconds.

